
The *x* in *xPU* stands for:
table { lll
  ~x~ ☰ ~stands for~ ☰ ~Typically used for~
  C ☰ Central ☰
  I ☰ Infrastructure ☰ Coordination of storage, networking, computional elements
  N ☰ Neural ☰
  G ☰ Graphics ☰ Graphics pipeline
  T ☰ Tensor ☰ Calculations with high dimensional arrays containing dense blocks (as often found in deep learning applications)
table }
